                <h1>Necessary Items for Your Background Check</h1>
                <p>For a background check, you'll need to provide personal information such as your full name, date of birth, and Social Security number. Additional documents may include a government-issued ID, proof of residency, and consent forms. Employers might also request details about your employment history and education.</p>
